title: From Forage to Fitness: Impacts of the Foodscape on Bighorn Sheep Demographics
text:
Hi there! I’m Alexis Means, a master’s student teaming up with the University of Idaho and the Oregon Department of Fish and Wildlife. Together, we’re diving into the wild world of bighorn sheep, exploring how their nutritional choices shape their populations. You could say I’m studying what’s on the menu for our fuzzy friends—and how it impacts their survival and growth!



John Day, Bighorn Sheep Capture - 2024
